data.description: Excellent opportunity in the Village of Bloomingdale, residential occupancy permits for each unit.  Property has commercial opportunities as well.   Property has a new roof and has been used a 2 unit rental for the past 10+ years. Rear unit has hardwood flooring, washer&dryer, separate heat, new water heater, and new carpet. Front unit possibly could be used as a business. Tile flooring throughout, open kitchen-living area concept, handicap accessible bathroom w/ walk in shower.
